<html>
    <header>
        <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width'/>
        <style>html, body, div { margin: 0px; padding: 0px; } html, body { width: 100%; height: 100%; }</style>
        <script>
          function dispatchToAAJSBridge(eventType) {
            if (window.SA_AD_JS_BRIDGE) {
              try {
                window.SA_AD_JS_BRIDGE[eventType]();
              } catch (error) {
                console.log('[AwesomeHtml]: dispatchToAAJSBridge error: ', error);
              }
            }
          }
        </script>
    </header>
    <body><script type="text/javascript" onload="dispatchToAAJSBridge()" onerror="dispatchToAAJSBridge('adFailedToLoad')" src="http://localhost:8080/yellow_box_ad.js"></script></body>
